'''Arlington Square Business Park''' is a [[business park]] in [[Bracknell]], [[England]], owned and operated by [[Goodman UK]].
The park houses a number of well-known companies, including [[Novell]], [[Fujitsu]] and [[Ally Financial|GMAC]].<ref>{{ cite web |url=http://www.arlingtonsquarebracknell.com/occupiers/overview.html |title=Arlington Square Occupiers |accessdate=2010-08-03 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100704190224/http://www.arlingtonsquarebracknell.com/occupiers/overview.html |archivedate=4 July 2010 |deadurl=yes |df= }}</ref>
